text: Stortorget is a public square in Gamla Stan, the old town in central Stockholm, Sweden. Stortorget may also refer to: * Gustaf Adolfs torg, Gothenburg, a town square in central Gothenburg, Sweden * Stortorget, Kalmar, the main square in Kalmar, Sweden * Stortorget, Karlskrona, the largest square in Karlskrona, Sweden * A square in Malmö, Sweden ==See also== * Stortorvet, Oslo, Norway * Old Great Square (Turku) (Swedish: Gamla Stortorget), in Turku, Finland
title: Stortorget (disambiguation)
